</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Madonna and Beatty? 
</P>
<P>
A Madonna rep tells us -- and production sources confirm -- that the
blond 
bombshell will play '30s nightclub singer-gangster's moll Breathless
Mahoney 
opposite Warren, who has the title role in the long-delayed "Dick
Tracy." 
</P>
<P>
As Breathless she'll sing at least two original songs, yet unwritten.
And 
she'll attempt to seduce the straight-laced copper away from lady love
Tess 
Trueheart, who is yet to be cast. 
</P>
<P>
Beatty produces/directs the $30 million-plus Touchstone film, to begin 
production in February, to be filmed on the Universal lot, according to 
sources. Craig Modderno 
</P>
