librarian what time the library closed. At 8:30, Railey, using a pay
phone, 
called home on a private line. Peggy Railey told him she was putting the 
children to bed. She then called her parents long distance in Tyler and
talked 
from 8:49 p.m. until 9:14 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
